Summary: Saw white light thru trees then it began flashing then it appeared to be a plane.
divs: Sighting DetailsI went out on my deck to smoke when I noticed what appeared to be a steady white light moving behind the trees as it neared me the light began to strobe then as it got closer I could tell it was a plane. I did video tape it but that is inconclusive at the moment.
